  "body": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Are you really <b><span style=\"color: #b300b3;\">fustrated</span></b> of <span style=\"color: #ff4d4d;\"><b>dying</b></span> just because of typing the <b><span style=\"color: #ff8000;\">gamemode</span></b> command not fast enough?</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><b>Then i have the <span style=\"color: #0080ff;\">perfect</span> plugin for you!</b></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Commands</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&bull; /gmc | /gm0 <strong>-- Change your gamemode to Creative</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&bull; /gms | /gm1<strong>&nbsp;-- Change your gamemode to Survival</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&bull; /gmp | /gm2<strong>&nbsp;-- Change your gamemode to Creative</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Donation</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #33cccc;\">Paypal:</span></strong> <strong>https://paypal.me/YM2IT</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ffcc00;\">Honeygain:</span>&nbsp;https://r.honeygain.me/DR3B6F8B0A</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><b>Buymeacoffee:&nbsp;</b></span></strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><b><span style=\"color: #000000;\">https://www.buymeacoffee.com/ym2it</span></b></span></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Media</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">(No videos yet)</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\nOther links\nBukkit: https://dev.bukkit.org/projects/new-easygamemodes\nSpigotMC: https://www.spigotmc.org/resources/easygamemodes.106296/\nPlugin made with Spigot Generator plugin in MCreator\nby\nLead Dev - Goldorion\nContributors: Klemen",
